<body>
<div style= "max-width: 1000px;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  padding-left: 10px;
  padding-right: 10px;">
<h2 style = "text-align: center; color: #35564C">
National Railway Delay Tracker
</h2>
<p>Dear Customer, 
<br> We are writing to inform of you a delay on your subscriptions. 
Please find the below service details for your future reference.
</p>
<table style="border: 1px solid black; float: left; width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
<tr style = "background-color: #009879;">
<th style= "padding: 15px;color: #ffffff; text-align: left;flex-basis: 10%;"> Origin Location </th>
<th style= "padding: 15px;color: #ffffff; text-align: left;flex-basis: 10%;"> Destination Location </th>
<th style= "padding: 15px;color: #ffffff; text-align: left;flex-basis: 10%;"> Leaving Time </th>
<th style= "padding: 15px;color: #ffffff; text-align: left;flex-basis: 10%;"> Arrival Time </th>
<th style= "padding: 15px;color: #ffffff; text-align: left;flex-basis: 10%;"> Service Type </th>
<th style= "padding: 15px;color: #ffffff; text-align: left;flex-basis: 10%;"> Service Id </th>
<th style= "padding: 15px;color: #ffffff; text-align: left;flex-basis: 10%;"> Delay Status </th>
<th style= "padding: 15px;color: #ffffff; text-align: left;flex-basis: 10%;"> Delay Time </th>
<th style= "padding: 15px;color: #ffffff; text-align: left;flex-basis: 10%;"> Delay Reason </th>
</tr>
<tr style= "background-color: #f3f3f3;border-bottom: 1px solid #dddddd;">
<td style= "padding: 15px;text-align: left;"> #[payload.originLocation] </td>
<td style= "padding: 15px;text-align: left;"> #[payload.destinationLocation] </td>
<td style= "padding: 15px;text-align: left;"> #[payload.fromTime] </td>
